How run the program:
 -Server ./chat
 -Client ./chat -s <IP address> -p <port number>
 
 You must start the server first. The server will display the IP address and Port
 that it wants you to connect to 
 
 
 Questions asked:
 -Can I hard code the port as long as it is above 1024 - YES
 
